ISLAMABAD, Aug 15 (APP): President Dr. Arif Alvi on Monday expressed his deep grief over the loss of precious lives in the church fire incident in Giza, Egypt and prayed for the prompt recovery of those injured in the unfortunate incident.
In a twitter post, the President also extended his heartfelt condolences to the bereaved families and the government of Egypt.
